WEBVTT

01:48:30.688 --> 01:48:34.223
Thousands of meerkats
on a floating
carnivorous island...

01:48:34.225 --> 01:48:36.326
and no one
has ever seen it?

01:48:36.328 --> 01:48:39.262
Yes, just like I told you.

01:48:39.264 --> 01:48:40.997
Bananas don't float.
(SPEAKING JAPANESE)

01:48:40.999 --> 01:48:42.832
Why are you talking
about bananas?

01:48:42.834 --> 01:48:45.602
You said the orangutan
floated to you
on a bundle of bananas.
